article.headline: Lipscomb 73, Nicholls State 71
article.story: WESTWEGO, La. (AP) -- Brian Fisk scored 22 points -- including a jumper with 2.4 seconds remaining in the game that proved to be the game-winning basket -- to lead Lipscomb to a 73-71 victory over Nicholls State Monday night. Shaun Durant and Jason Guyette added 13 points each for the Bisons (7-4). Durant also grabbed nine rebounds. Eddie Ard finished with 11 points. Michael Czepil led the Colonels (2-7) with 16 points. Stefan Blaszczynski added 12 and Kevin Goffney had 10. Goffney also pulled down seven rebounds.
